{"tid":1280632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"向政府重申：回應訴求先有用！咩嘗試溝通係晒鳩氣！","createTime":"2019-07-03T04:50:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T10:26:31.000Z","uid":2617,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a5ee5fd2a23509d2608e9459be92c60a56bcc262","tid":1280632,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:50:47.000Z","msg":"見到咩消息人士話會透過中間人<br />\n嘗試溝通同了解年輕人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我屌你老母</span></span><br />\n年青人既訴求已經表達得清清楚楚<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求+政制改革雙普選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n你同邊個年輕人溝通都係會得到呢個結論<br />\n我地已經命都唔要 個訴求仲唔夠清晰響亮？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你老母你地冇人識上網？<br />\n冇人識去下各大代表年青人既討論區睇下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（例如babykingdom）<br />\n<br />\n咩嘗試溝通<br />\n只係你班冷酷無情既高層<br />\n試圖擺姿態做SHOW 緩和民情 既手段<br />\n你真係有誠意既<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔該確切真誠地正面回應以上所有訴求<br />\n否則所有BK同香討既義士<br />\n絕對唔會停止抗爭 堅持到底<br />\n我怕佢地甚至採取更強硬既手段<br />\n極權政府必要付上沉重代價<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n謝謝大家"},{"pid":"25c6f5acbbf42efac51f1db1de289ba38ff1d416","tid":1280632,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:52:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94a1298e443452ab36c3d2244207a476237b2b18","tid":1280632,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:56:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72cda2f7b0db2555a1d1843edc7ac1d307995c43","tid":1280632,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T05:05:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aafeea9bbbbcb5ef6d04f725